@startuml Supplier State Machine
title Supplier Lifecycle - State Machine Diagram
left to right direction

skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor#E8EAF6
    BorderColor#3F51B5
    ArrowColor#424242
}

[*] --> PENDING : Manager creates supplier

PENDING --> ACTIVE : Manager approves
PENDING --> REJECTED : Manager rejects

ACTIVE --> INACTIVE : Manager deactivates
ACTIVE --> SUSPENDED : Policy violation

INACTIVE --> ACTIVE : Manager reactivates
INACTIVE --> SUSPENDED : Policy violation

SUSPENDED --> ACTIVE : Manager reinstates
SUSPENDED --> REJECTED : Manager rejects

REJECTED --> [*]

note right of ACTIVE
  Can supply products
  Inventory replenishment
  Orders can be placed
end note

note right of SUSPENDED
  No new orders
  Existing orders paused
  Requires review
end note

@enduml
